---js
const tags = "pages";
const eleventyNavigation = {
key: "Home",
order: 1
};
---

<div class="container mx-auto max-w-5xl px-4">

	<!-- Hero: Intro -->
	<section class="grid md:grid-cols-5 gap-8 md:gap-12 py-12 md:py-16">
		<div class="md:col-span-3 space-y-6">
			<h1 class="font-serif text-heading text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-5xl font-bold tracking-tight">
				Hi! I'm Noel. Software designer and developer.
			</h1>

			<p class="font-thin text-xl md:text-2xl leading-relaxed">
				I help climate startup founders turn ideas into working software — from concept to launch and beyond.
			</p>

			<p class="font-thin text-base md:text-lg text-body-subtle leading-relaxed">
				I combine a design background with 20 years of software engineering experience.
			</p>

			<ul class="font-thin space-y-3 text-base text-body">
				<li class="flex items-start">
					<span class="mr-3">•</span>
					<span>I bring clarity to what you should build and why, in the language of your domain.</span>
				</li>
				<li class="flex items-start">
					<span class="mr-3">•</span>
					<span>I build it with you, as a thought partner who absorbs the risk and guarantees results.</span>
				</li>
			</ul>
		</div>

		<div class="md:col-span-2">
			<div class="md:sticky md:top-8">
				<img
					src="/img/noel-landscape-768.jpg"
					alt="Portrait of Noel"
					class="w-full max-w-md h-auto rounded-lg shadow-lg md:hidden border-1 border-c04"
				/>
				<img
					src="/img/noel-portrait-500.jpg"
					alt="Portrait of Noel"
					class="w-full h-auto rounded-lg shadow-lg hidden md:block border-1 border-c04"
				/>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<!-- Pulled in all directions -->
	<section class="grid md:grid-cols-5 gap-8 md:gap-12 py-12 md:py-16">
		<div class="md:col-span-3 space-y-6">
			<h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold font-serif text-heading tracking-tight">
				Your software project shouldn't be one more source of chaos.
			</h2>

			<p class="font-thin text-lg md:text-xl">
				You have too many open questions, unclear priorities, and no confidence in what to do next. Every week of uncertainty is a week of lost momentum.
			</p>

			<p class="font-thin text-lg md:text-xl text-body leading-relaxed">
				Let's fix that.
			</p>
		</div>

		<div class="md:col-span-2 hidden md:block">
			<div class="md:sticky md:top-8">
				<img
					src="/img/entangled.png"
					alt="Abstract representation of entangled communications and processes"
					class="w-full max-w-sm h-auto rounded-lg drop-shadow-md"
				/>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<!-- The promise: Clarity and focus -->
	<section class="grid md:grid-cols-5 gap-8 md:gap-12 py-12 md:py-16">
		<div class="md:col-span-3 space-y-6">
			<h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold font-serif text-heading tracking-tight">
				Get clarity on your software project, in a week
			</h2>

			<p class="font-thin text-lg md:text-xl">
				Imagine having a clear picture of where your project actually stands; a concrete plan you can act on immediately.
			</p>

			<ul class="font-thin space-y-3 text-base md:text-lg text-body">
				<li class="flex items-start">
					<span class="mr-3">•</span>
					<span>Know which problems are worth your time and what to say no to.</span>
				</li>
				<li class="flex items-start">
					<span class="mr-3">•</span>
					<span>Understand your options (custom build, off-the-shelf, or a mix) and the trade-offs of each.</span>
				</li>
				<li class="flex items-start">
					<span class="mr-3">•</span>
					<span>Know what to do when a dev process has gone sideways.</span>
				</li>
				<li class="flex items-start">
					<span class="mr-3">•</span>
					<span>Get answers in terms that make sense to you, not developer jargon.</span>
				</li>
				<li class="flex items-start">
					<span class="mr-3">•</span>
					<span>Walk away with a document you can hand to any team, vendor, or funder.</span>
				</li>
			</ul>

			<p class="font-thin text-base md:text-lg">
				That's what I deliver in the <a href="/services/clarity-workshop/" class="underline underline-offset-4 decoration-orange text-orange transition-colors font-normal">Clarity Workshop</a>, in about a week, with 3-4 hours of your time.
			</p>
		</div>

		<div class="md:col-span-2 hidden md:block">
			<div class="md:sticky md:top-8">
					<img
					src="/img/fungi-roots-clean.png"
					alt="Digital fungi grow on the understory of a lush forest."
					class="w-full max-w-sm h-auto rounded-lg drop-shadow-md"
				/>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<!-- The relationship: A thought partner -->
	<section class="grid md:grid-cols-5 gap-8 md:gap-12 py-12 md:py-16">
		<div class="md:col-span-3 space-y-6">
			<h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold font-serif text-heading tracking-tight">
				When you're ready to build, do it with a thought partner
			</h2>

			<p class="font-thin text-lg md:text-xl">
				I handle design and engineering, think strategically with you, and absorb project risk.
			</p>

			<ul class="font-thin space-y-3 text-base md:text-lg text-body">
				<li class="flex items-start">
					<span class="mr-3">•</span>
					<span>We talk in a language that is meaningful to you.</span>
				</li>
				<li class="flex items-start">
					<span class="mr-3">•</span>
					<span>Your vision stays intact — one person ensures every detail aligns with it.</span>
				</li>
				<li class="flex items-start">
					<span class="mr-3">•</span>
					<span>Fixed-price milestones with clear success criteria. You pay for results, not hours.</span>
				</li>
				<li class="flex items-start">
					<span class="mr-3">•</span>
					<span>A bug-free guarantee — I keep going until the milestone goals are met, regardless of effort.</span>
				</li>
			</ul>

			<p class="font-thin text-base md:text-lg">
				You delegate the strategic and technical weight to someone who can carry it. You'll never have to explain a runaway cost or product flop to your board.
			</p>
		</div>

		<div class="md:col-span-2 hidden md:block">
			<div class="md:sticky md:top-8">
				<img
					src="/img/cabin.png"
					alt="A cabin in the woods"
					class="w-full max-w-sm h-auto rounded-lg drop-shadow-md"
				/>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<!-- Credibility -->
	<section class="py-12 md:py-16 rounded-lg md:bg-gradient-to-b md:from-ground md:to-c01 md:ring-3 md:ring-c01 md:shadow-lg">
		<div class="max-w-xl m-auto space-y-6">
			<h2 class="text-orange text-3xl md:text-4xl font-serif font-bold tracking-tight">
				20 years of design + engineering, focused on climate tech
			</h2>

			<p class="font-thin text-lg md:text-xl">
				I combine a design background with two decades of software engineering. A designer sees design problems. A developer sees code problems. I look at the whole picture.
			</p>

			<p class="font-thin text-base md:text-lg text-body-subtle">
				I work exclusively with climate tech founders because I believe the work matters. That means you're talking to someone who understands your mission, your constraints, and the specific ways software projects can go wrong.
			</p>

			<p class="font-thin text-base md:text-lg text-body">
				That experience is why I can bear the risk of offering guarantees, and why I've been providing them for years.
			</p>
		</div>
	</section>

	<!-- CTA: Start with the Clarity Workshop -->
	<section class="my-16 md:my-24">
		<div class="flex gap-24 md:gap-8 flex-wrap md:flex-nowrap flex-col-reverse md:flex-row">

			<div class="grow rounded-lg border bg-white/5 border-1 border-c03 shadow-xl p-6 md:p-8"
				id="free-call">
				<h2 class="text-3xl md:text-3xl font-serif font-bold tracking-tight mb-6 text-body">
					Start with a week of clarity
				</h2>

				<p class="font-thin text-base md:text-lg text-body-subtle mb-4">
					The <a href="/services/clarity-workshop/" class="underline underline-offset-4 decoration-orange text-orange transition-colors font-normal">Clarity Workshop</a> is the best first step. In a few focused conversations over about a week, I review your situation through a product, design, and engineering lens — and give you a clear plan you can act on immediately.
				</p>

				<p class="font-thin text-base md:text-lg text-body-subtle mb-4">
					<span class="font-normal">1 free spot left.</span> I'm running the workshop at no cost with one more founder, in exchange for honest feedback.
				</p>

				<p class="font-thin text-base md:text-lg text-body-subtle mb-6">
					Schedule a 30-minute discovery call to see if it's a fit. No sales pressure — if it's not right, I'll tell you.
				</p>

				<!--
				<a href="https://calendar.app.google/EvzyJeS767M8bgcQ7" class="inline-block border-1 border-orange bg-orange hover:px-12 transition-all duration-500 ease-in-out text-ground font-medium px-6 py-3 rounded-lg">
					Schedule a free discovery call
				</a>
				-->
				<div class="flex gap-4">
					<a href="/services/clarity-workshop/" class="inline-block border-1 border-orange bg-orange hover:px-12 transition-all duration-500 ease-in-out text-ground font-medium px-6 py-3 rounded-lg text-center">
						Tell me more
					</a>
					<a href="https://calendar.app.google/EvzyJeS767M8bgcQ7" class="inline-block border-1 border-c03 bg-c01 hover:px-12 transition-all duration-500 ease-in-out text-c06 font-medium px-6 py-3 rounded-lg text-center">
						Schedule free call now
					</a>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div class="max-w-none md:max-w-2/5 rounded-lg p-6 md:p-8 shadow-sm">
				<div class="flex">
					<div class="text-8xl font-serif font-bold text-orange">&quot;</div>
					<div>

						<p class="text-c06 md:text-lg mb-4">
							We have been working with Noel for over three years. He's communicative, responsive and a great developer.
						</p>

						<p class="font-thin text-c06 md:text-lg mb-4">
							Noel developed a fit-for-purpose platform that has allowed us to build and maintain our tools relatively independently despite having very little technical expertise. He's helped us expand the platform, think about how to better serve our users, and find ways to improve it.
						</p>

						<p class="font-thin font-serif text-c06 text-sm md:text-base font-bold text-orange">
							— Maria Lucien. Program Associate, People Powered
						</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<!-- Portfolio fallback -->
	<section class="my-12 md:my-16">
		<div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-start md:items-center gap-4">
			<p class="font-thin text-base md:text-lg text-body-subtle">
				Not ready to schedule a call? <span class="font-normal">Explore some of my work:</span>
			</p>
			<a href="/portfolio/" class="md:text-lg p-2 border-1 border-c02 hover:bg-c01 transition-colors shadow-md rounded-md">
				Portfolio ➡️
			</a>
		</div>
	</section>
</div>
